\c 12
\s Umfanekiso wabalimi besivini
\p
\v 1 Waseqala ukukhuluma labo ngemifanekiso \add wathi\add*: Umuntu wahlanyela isivini, wasibiyela ngothango, wagebha isikhamelo, wakha umphotshongo, wasiqhatshisa kubalimi, waya kwelinye ilizwe.
\v 2 Kwathi sekuyisikhathi esifaneleyo wathuma inceku kubalimi, ukuze yemukele kubalimi okwesithelo sesivini.
\v 3 Kodwa ba\add yi\add*bamba bayitshaya, ba\add yi\add*mukisa ize.
\v 4 Wasebuya ethuma kubo enye inceku; laleyo bayitshaya ngamatshe ba\add yi\add*limaza ekhanda, ba\add yi\add*xotsha \add isi\add*thelwe inhloni.
\v 5 Wasebuya ethuma enye; yona basebeyibulala; lezinye ezinengi, ezinye bazitshaya, lezinye bazibulala\x + Mat. 21.33-46. Luka 20.9-19.\x*.
\v 6 Ngakho eseselendodana eyodwa ethandekayo kuye\x + Luka 20.13. Mat. 3.17.\x*, ekucineni wayithuma kubo layo, esithi: Bazayihlonipha indodana yami.
\v 7 Kodwa labobalimi bakhulumisana besithi: Le yindlalifa; wozani, siyibulale, lelifa lizakuba ngelethu.
\v 8 Basebe\add yi\add*bamba bayibulala, ba\add yi\add*phosela ngaphandle kwesivini.
\v 9 Ngakho uzakwenzani umninisivini? Uzakuza ababhubhise abalimi, anikele isivini kwabanye\x + Mat. 21.41. Luka 20.16.\x*.
\v 10 Kalibalanga yini lumbhalo \add othi\add*: Ilitshe abakhi abalalayo, yilo eseliyinhloko yengonsi;
\v 11 lokhu kwenziwe yiNkosi, njalo kuyisimanga emehlweni ethu\x + Hlab. 118.22,23.\x*?
\v 12 Basebedinga ukumbamba, kodwa besaba ixuku; ngoba babesazi ukuthi wayekhulume lumfanekiso emelane labo\x + 11.18.\x*. Basebemtshiya bahamba\x + Mat. 22.22.\x*.
\s Umthelo kaKesari
\p
\v 13 Basebethuma kuye abanye babaFarisi labakaHerodi\x + Mat. 22.15-45. Luka 20.20-38.\x*, ukuze bamthiye ekukhulumeni\x + Luka 11.54.\x*.
\v 14 Basebesiza bathi kuye: Mfundisi, siyazi ukuthi wena uqotho, njalo kawukhathali ngomuntu; ngoba kawunanzi isimo somuntu, kodwa ufundisa indlela kaNkulunkulu ngeqiniso\x + 12.32. Luka 20.21.\x*: Kuvunyelwe yini ukuthela kuKesari kumbe hatshi?
\v 15 Sithele, kumbe singatheli? Kodwa ekwazi ukuzenzisa kwabo wathi kubo: Lingilingelani\x + Joha. 8.6.\x*? Lethani kimi \w udenariyo\w**, ukuze ngibone.
\v 16 Basebeletha. Wasesithi kubo: Ngokabani lumfanekiso lalumbhalo\x + Mat. 22.20.\x*? Basebesithi kuye: NgokaKesari.
\v 17 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Mnikeni uKesari okukaKesari, loNkulunkulu okukaNkulunkulu. Basebemangala ngaye.
\s Ukuvuka kwabafileyo
\p
\v 18 Basebesiza kuye abaSadusi, abathi kakukho ukuvuka \add kwabafileyo\add*; basebembuza, besithi:
\v 19 Mfundisi, uMozisi wasibhalela, \add ukuthi\add*: Uba umfowabo womuntu esifa, atshiye umka\add khe\add*, engatshiyi bantwana, umfowabo kamthathe umkakhe, amvusele umfowabo inzalo\x + Dute. 25.5.\x*;
\v 20 kwakulezelamani eziyisikhombisa; owokuqala wasethatha umfazi, wafa engatshiyanga inzalo;
\v 21 lowesibili wamthatha, wafa, laye engatshiyanga inzalo; lowesithathu kwaba njalo;
\v 22 lalaba boyisikhombisa bamthatha, kabatshiyanga inzalo. Ekucineni kwabo bonke kwafa lomfazi.
\v 23 Ngakho ekuvukeni \add kwabafileyo\add*, mhla bevukayo, uzakuba ngumkabani kubo; lokhu abayisikhombisa babelaye engumkabo?
\v 24 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Kaliduhanga yini ngalokhu, ngoba lingayazi imibhalo, loba amandla kaNkulunkulu?
\v 25 Ngoba mhla bevukayo ekufeni, kabathathani, njalo kabendiswa, kodwa banjengengilosi ezisemazulwini.
\v 26 Kodwa mayelana labafileyo, ukuthi bayavuswa, kalifundanga yini egwalweni lukaMozisi, ukuthi uNkulunkulu esihlahleni wakhuluma njani kuye\x + Luka 20.37. Roma 11.2.\x*, esithi: NginguNkulunkulu kaAbrahama, loNkulunkulu kaIsaka, loNkulunkulu kaJakobe\x + Eks. 3.6.\x*?
\v 27 Kayisuye uNkulunkulu wabafileyo, kodwa uNkulunkulu wabaphilayo; ngakho lina liduhile kakhulu.
\s Umlayo wokuqala
\p
\v 28 Wasefika omunye wababhali, esezwile bebuzana, esebonile ukuthi ubaphendule kuhle, wambuza \add wathi\add*: Yiwuphi umlayo wokuqala kuyo yonke\x + Luka 20.39.\x*?
\v 29 UJesu wasemphendula wathi: Owokuqala kuyo yonke imilayo \add ngowokuthi\add*: Zwana, Israyeli: INkosi uNkulunkulu wethu, iNkosi yinye;
\v 30 njalo wothanda iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho ngenhliziyo yakho yonke, langomphefumulo wakho wonke, langengqondo yakho yonke, langamandla akho wonke. Yilo umlayo owokuqala\x + Dute. 6.4,5.\x*.
\v 31 Lowesibili uyafanana, yilo: Wothanda umakhelwane wakho njengalokhu uzi\add thanda wena\x + Levi 19.18.\x*\add*. Kawukho omunye umlayo omkhulu kulale.
\v 32 Umbhali wasesithi kuye: Kuhle, Mfundisi, utsho okuqotho ukuthi kuloNkulunkulu oyedwa\x + 12.14.\x*, langaphandle kwakhe kakho omunye;
\v 33 lokumthanda ngenhliziyo yonke\x + Dute. 4.35.\x*, langokuqedisisa konke, langomphefumulo wonke, langamandla wonke, lokuthanda umakhelwane njengawe\x + Luka 2.47. Kol. 1.9.\x*, kuyedlula yonke\x + 1 Sam. 15.22.\x* iminikelo yokutshiswa lemihlatshelo\x + Hlab. 40.6. Heb. 10.6,8.\x*.
\v 34 UJesu esembona ukuthi uphendule ngenhlakanipho, wathi kuye: Kawukhatshana lombuso kaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 25.24.\x*. Njalo kakwabe kusaba khona umuntu olesibindi sokumbuza\x + Mat. 22.46. Luka 20.40.\x*.
\s UKristu losendo lwakhe
\p
\v 35 UJesu\x + Luka 20.41-44.\x*, efundisa ethempelini\x + Mat. 26.55.\x*, wasephendula wathi: Batsho njani ababhali ukuthi uKristu uyindodana kaDavida?
\v 36 Ngoba uDavida uqobo lwakhe ngoMoya oyiNgcwele wathi: INkosi yathi eNkosini yami: Hlala ngakwesokunene sami, ngize ngibeke izitha zakho zibe yisenabelo senyawo zakho\x + Hlab. 110.1.\x*.
\v 37 Ngakho uDavida uqobo lwakhe umbiza \add ngokuthi\add* yiNkosi; pho uyindodana yakhe njani?
\p Lexuku elikhulu lamuzwa ngokuthokoza\x + 6.20.\x*.
\s UJesu usola ababhali
\p
\v 38 Wasesithi kubo ekufundiseni kwakhe\x + 4.2.\x*: Qaphelani ababhali\x + Luka 20.45-47. Mat. 23.5.\x*, abathanda ukuhamba bembethe izembatho ezinde\x + 16.5.\x*, lokubingelelwa emidangeni\x + Mat. 23.6,7.\x*\x + Luka 11.43.\x*,
\v 39 lezihlalo eziqakathekileyo emasinagogeni\x + Mat. 23.6, 7.\x*, lezihlalo zabahloniphekayo ekudleni kwantambama\x + Mat. 23.6,7.\x*\x + Luka 11.43.\x*;
\v 40 abadla izindlu zabafelokazi, bekhuleka \add isikhathi\add* eside ngokuzenzisa; laba bazakwemukela ukulahlwa okukhulu\x + Mat. 23.14.\x*.
\s Umnikelo womfelokazi
\p
\v 41 UJesu wasehlala phansi\x + Luka 21.1-4.\x* maqondana lesitsha somnikelo wabona ukuthi ixuku liphosela njani imali\x + Joha. 8.20. Neh. 13.4,5.\x*\f + \fk imali: \ft uhlamvu lwemali yethusi; bona Mat. 10.9\f* esitsheni somnikelo\x + 2 Kho. 12.9.\x*; labanothileyo abanengi baphosela okunengi.
\v 42 Kwasekufika umfelokazi othile ongumyanga waphosela inhlamvana ezimbili ezincane zemali, eziyindibilitshi\x + Mat. 5.26.\x*.
\v 43 Wasebizela kuye abafundi bakhe, wathi kubo: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Lumfelokazi ongumyanga uphosele okwedlula bonke\x + 2 Kor. 8.12.\x* laba abaphoseleyo esitsheni somnikelo\x + Joha. 8.20. Neh. 13.4,5.\x*;
\v 44 ngoba bonke baphosele kokunengi kwabo; kodwa yena ebuyangeni bakhe\x + Fil. 4.11.\x* uphosele konke alakho, konke okwempilo yakhe\x + Luka 8.43; 15.12,30; 21.4. 1 Joha. 3.17. Dute. 24.6.\x*.
